# VeighNa框架的华鑫奇点柜台接口

<p align="center">
  <img src ="https://vnpy.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/vnpy-logo.png"/>
</p>

<p align="center">
    <img src ="https://img.shields.io/badge/version-2025.04.16-blueviolet.svg"/>
